                        .modal-content
                            .box
                                .modal-card-title
                                    p(style="margin-bottom: 0.4rem;") Nikhil Gupta
                                    span #[span.tag.is-warning.is-light.nohuechange Tester] #[span.tag.is-danger.is-light.nohuechange Developer]
                                br
                                p #[strong Nikhil Gupta] ("not" Ruhan's brother) has also been with Siddhant since the beginning. Throughout the development of Vocabustudy, he has #[strong requested features] to make Vocabustudy better. He #[strong created the Discord server], #[strong invited people], and #[moderates it]. He and Omkar have #[strong shared Vocabustudy with the world], which has helped grow it along the way.
