        br
        h2.title.is2 Thank you for your donations! Even a dollar can help us improve this website.
    .page#discord(data-nosnippet)
        h1 Discord
        p.title.is-size-5 Vocabustudy Discord Server
        p Have you joined our Discord server yet? There's free homework help, support, bots, and more!
        p The server in completely student-run, and Nikhil, Omkar, and Siddhant do not endorse it. The server is moderation by Nikhil Gupta, Omkar Patil, and Ruhan Gupta, in addition to our team of moderators and helpers.
        p For any questions about the Discord server, please contact "OP#1192" or "Nikhilatvocabustudy#4578" in Discord, or email #[a(href="mailto:management@vocabustudy.org") management@vocabustudy.org].
        p If you wish to join, you can join #[a(href="https://discord.gg/UrRs7Bbr6d") here].
        h1 YouTube:
        p That's right, we have a YouTube channel!
        P You can find our channel #[a(href="https://www.youtube.com/@forzero") here].
    .page.realhome#home
        div.custom-scrollbar
            div
                div
                    div
                        h2.is-size-2 Learn Vocabulary, #[br]For Free.
                        ul
                            li 100% Free
                            li No Ads
                            li Relevant Vocab
                    p.mb-0.is-size-5.has-text-weight-bold(style="margin-top: 2rem;") Created/developed by Siddhant Kameswar
                    p.my-0.is-size-6 #[a.has-text-white.is-size-5.has-text-weight-bold(href="/#credits" style="border-bottom: 1px solid white;") Credits]
                    p.mb-0.mt-4.mdc-typography--overline.is-size-7 VOCABUSTUDY - U STUDY VOCAB
                        br
                        button.button.is-ghost.btn-show-features(style="color: white;")
                            span.icon.is-small
                                i.material-symbols-rounded keyboard_double_arrow_down
            div.home-features
                div
                    h2.is-size-4 Features:
                    ul.list.has-text-white.is-filled
                        li.list-item
                            div.list-item-image
                                span.icon
                                    i.material-symbols-rounded tune
